Dialogue: Are you going to VIRIDIAN FOREST? Be careful, it's a natural maze!
RATTATA may be small, but its bite is wicked! Did you get one?
I came here with some friends! They're out for POKEMON fights!
I ran out of POKE BALLs to catch POKEMON with! You should carry extras!

name: Signpost 1
Dialogue: TRAINER TIPS Weaken POKEMON before attempting capture! When healthy, they may escape!

name: Signpost 2
Dialogue: For poison, use ANTIDOTE! Get it at POKEMON MARTs!

name: Signpost 3
Dialogue: TRAINER TIPS If you want to avoid battles, stay away from grassy areas!

name: Signpost 4
Dialogue: TRAINER TIPS Contact PROF.OAK via PC to get your POKEDEX evaluated!

name: Signpost 5
Dialogue: TRAINER TIPS No stealing of POKEMON from other trainers! Catch only wild POKEMON!
Have you noticed the bushes on the roadside? They can be cut down by a special POKEMON move.
Many POKEMON live only in forests and caves. You need to look everywhere to get different kinds!

name: Trainer 1
Dialogue: Hey! You have POKEMON! Come on! Let's battle'em [sic]!

name: Trainer 1 after
Dialogue: Ssh! You'll scare the bugs away!

name: Trainer 2
Dialogue: Yo! You can't jam out if you're a POKEMON trainer!

name: Trainer 2 after
Dialogue: Darn! I'm going to catch some stronger ones!

name: Trainer 3
Dialogue: Hey, wait up! What's the hurry?

name: Trainer 3 after
Dialogue: Sometimes, you can find stuff on the ground! I'm looking for the stuff I dropped!

name: Diglett 1
Dialogue:
What a surprise! DIGLETTs dug this long tunnel! It goes right to 
VIRIDIAN CITY!

name: Diglett 2
Dialogue:
I went to ROCK TUNNEL, but it's dark and scary. If a POKEMON's FLASH 
could light it up...

name: New 1
Dialogue: A fainted POKEMON can't fight. But, it can still use moves like CUT!

name: New 2
Dialogue: I'm looking for ABRA! Wanna trade one for MR.MIME?
Awww! Oh well...
What? That's not ABRA! If you get one, come back here!
Okay, connect the cable like so!
Hey thanks!

name: New 3
Dialogue: Once a POKEMON learns FLASH, you can get through ROCK TUNNEL.

name: New 4
Dialogue:
Hi! Remember me? I'm PROF.OAK's AIDE! If you caught 10 kinds 
of POKEMON, I'm supposed to give you an Hm05! So, Player! Have you 
caught at least 10 kinds of POKEMON?
Oh. I see. When you get 10 kinds, come back for HM05.

Great! You have caught <##> kinds of POKEMON! Congratulations! 
Here you go!
Oh! I see you don't have any room for the HM05.
The HM FLASH lights even the darkest dungeons.
